description:
This is a 23 minute workout called '20 MIN PILATES CORE & ABS WORKOUT || At-Home Pilates For All Levels' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Get ready to work and strengthen your core in this 20 Minute Pilates Core & Abs Workout. This class is a slower paced class designed to cater to all levels, providing lots of different variations depending on where you are in your pilates practice.
